Package: gau
Version: 2.2.4
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/lc/gau
Description: Fetch known URLs from AlienVault OTX, Wayback Machine, Common Crawl
 gau (getallurls) fetches known URLs from AlienVault's Open Threat Exchange,
 the Wayback Machine, Common Crawl and URLScan for any given domain.
 Inspired by Tomnomnom's waybackurls.
